data.description: This home offers many desirable features; a large corner lot with fenced back yard, open formal living and formal dining areas, the kitchen has an island work counter and opens to the breakfast area and family area with fireplace.  The spacious primary bedroom and primary bath with lots of closet space provide a great quiet corner for the owners.  The upstairs landing opens to the living/dining areas on the first floor.  All the rooms on the second floor, the two bedrooms, the second bath, laundry, and game room line up around the second-floor landing.  Finally, the location of the enclosed game room will allow you to enjoy your entertainment and not disturb the rest of the household.  Outside, the fenced back yard has a patio and gazebo for you to entertain or just kick back and relax. There is power to the storage shed.  Maybe with a little tweaking a workshop?  This home offers a package of features you just might fall in love with.
